docs.lead_paragraph: At the meeting of the American Therapeutic Society at Washington last week Dr. OLIVER T. OSBORNE read a paper on "The Strenuous Life," a life Which he considers to be pernicious rather than beneficent. If the essay shall cause a single pedestrian to be more considerate of the health of chauffeurs and horsemen it will not have been read and reported in vain.
